<a name="1" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub11103476_1" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="故事内容" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">境界的彼方</span>故事内容</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="1" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">一个偶然的契机，人类和妖梦之间出生的少年——<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%A5%9E%E5%8E%9F%E7%A7%8B%E4%BA%BA">神原秋人</a>，有一天与在学校屋顶看上去要跳楼的少女——<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%A0%97%E5%B1%B1%E6%9C%AA%E6%9D%A5">栗山未来</a>相遇了。有着即使在异界士中也很特殊的“血”之能力的少女，在孤独中战斗着。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">“我——看起来像是普通的人类么？”</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">少年决心帮助这个命运与自己重叠的少女。由此，围绕在少年身边险恶的战斗开始了。<sup>[2-3]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[2-3]_11103476">&nbsp;</a>
</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="2" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub11103476_2" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="登场角色" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">境界的彼方</span>登场角色</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="2" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="anchor-list">
<a name="2_1" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub11103476_2_1" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="主要角色" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="2-1" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">境界的彼方</span>主要角色</h3>
</div>
<table log-set-param="table_view" class="table-view log-set-param transparentBorder" data-sort="sortDisabled"><tr><td width="326" height="417" align="left" valign="top"><div class="para" label-module="para"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%A0%97%E5%B1%B1%E6%9C%AA%E6%9D%A5"><b>栗山未来</b></a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">配音演员：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%A7%8D%E7%94%B0%E6%A2%A8%E6%B2%99">种田梨沙</a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">本作女主角，高中一年级生。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">拥有操纵血的能力的异界士，实力强大。但是这种能力被认为是异界士中的异端，因此被他人敬而远之。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">曾经被伊波家收养。盆栽（狂热）爱好者，吃货。口头禅是“我不高兴です 或 不愉快ですPS:です表示口头禅语气词”，但并非真不高兴。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">小说中因虚无之影杀死了伊波唯，以为会被青梅竹马真诚优斗憎恨于是来到了虚无之影可能出现的城镇（即故事发生地）。后来与优斗解开心结归入名濑家族旗下。认为自己是被诅咒的一族而不能与他人一样普通地生活，内心孤独。遇到神原秋人后身边渐渐地也围聚了朋友，随秋人加入文艺部。对秋人有好感。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">动画中因为杀死了伊波唯，内心有阴影，而难以对妖梦下杀手，也因此收入来源被切断，生活十分贫穷。在彩华的照相馆里当模特赚外快。真正目的是消减妖梦境界的彼方（神原秋人），然而却无法对神原秋人下杀手，选择牺牲自己（牺牲不是指死去）将境界的彼方驱逐出秋人的身体。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">小说中对秋人有好感，动画中明确喜欢秋人。</div>
</td><td width="329" height="417" align="left" valign="top"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E5%A2%83%E7%95%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%BC%E6%96%B9/82347/0/e7cd7b899e510fb36de9c3abda33c895d1430c1d?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="栗山未来" style="width:220px;height:173px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="http://c.hiphotos.baidu.com/baike/s%3D220/sign=23f91606334e251fe6f7e3fa9787c9c2/e7cd7b899e510fb36de9c3abda33c895d1430c1d.jpg"  alt="栗山未来" style="width:220px;height:173px;"/>
</a>
<span class="description">
栗山未来
</span>
</div></div>
</td></tr><tr><td width="326" height="0" align="left" valign="top"><div class="para" label-module="para"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%A5%9E%E5%8E%9F%E7%A7%8B%E4%BA%BA"><b>神原秋人</b></a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">配音演员：<a target=_blank href="/item/KENN">KENN</a>（小学时代：田中芽衣）</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">故事主人公。文艺部部员，高中2年级生。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">母亲是异界士，父亲是不死的妖梦，自身是半妖的存在，继承其父不死的特性。（不死是再生能力极其强大）</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">其实连自己都不太清楚自己的身世。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">因为身份独特，所以无论在异界士中也好妖梦中也好都感到十分孤独，在这样的状况下生存了下来。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">眼镜控兼眼镜美少女控，动画中在彩华的照相馆购买未来的照片。自称是个能为眼镜和眼镜美少女赴汤蹈火的变态。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">对性格过于活泼的母亲充满无奈。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">在受到剧烈打击处于濒死状态时，体内妖梦的意识就会觉醒，实力异常强大，动画中能秒杀名濑博臣、新堂彩华、二之宫雫三人，除了栗山未来之外暂时没有人能战胜妖梦化后的神原秋人（但也只是让其恢复意识，并没有正面战斗）。小说中妖梦部分未知详细，动画中妖梦部分被认为是比虚空之影更为强大的妖梦——境界的彼方的另一部分。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">对未来有好感但不明确，动画中则是确实喜欢未来。</div>
</td><td valign="top" align="left" width="329"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-center" style="width:220px; float: none; display: block; margin: 0px auto; clear: both;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E5%A2%83%E7%95%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%BC%E6%96%B9/82347/0/3b87e950352ac65c09a515bafaf2b21192138a52?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="神原秋人" style="width:220px;height:166px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="http://b.hiphotos.baidu.com/baike/s%3D220/sign=8812e61509fa513d55aa6bdc0d6f554c/3b87e950352ac65c09a515bafaf2b21192138a52.jpg"  alt="神原秋人" style="width:220px;height:166px;"/>
</a>
<span class="description">
神原秋人
</span>
</div></div>
</td></tr><tr><td width="326" height="0" align="left" valign="top" class="coloredcell"><div class="para" label-module="para"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%90%8D%E6%BF%91%E7%BE%8E%E6%9C%88"><b>名濑美月</b></a></div>
配音演员：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%8C%85%E5%8E%9F%E5%AE%9E%E9%87%8C">茅原实里</a><div class="para" label-module="para">作为异界士中名门望族名濑家的次女。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">文艺部部长，高中2年级生。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">身负监视秋人的任务。实际上却十分担心秋人。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">同样对未来也满是担忧。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">是与秋人推心置腹的朋友。平时是抖S的言行。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">十分擅长吐槽。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">动画中自小被姐姐教育“身为异界士都是孤独的”，尽管内心充满渴望但从未参加灯会。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">小说中未见其用过除了结界以外的招数，动画中有一只名为“烤红薯”的妖梦，通常使用它来攻击。（小说中是峰岸舞耶的宠物妖梦的名字）</div>
</td><td valign="top" align="left" width="329"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-center" style="width:220px; float: none; display: block; margin: 0px auto; clear: both;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E5%A2%83%E7%95%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%BC%E6%96%B9/82347/0/a6efce1b9d16fdfae90bbb27b58f8c5495ee7b97?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="名濑美月" style="width:220px;height:176px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="http://g.hiphotos.baidu.com/baike/s%3D220/sign=7cdda1a9342ac65c63056171cbf3b21d/a6efce1b9d16fdfae90bbb27b58f8c5495ee7b97.jpg"  alt="名濑美月" style="width:220px;height:176px;"/>
</a>
<span class="description">
名濑美月
</span>
</div></div>
</td></tr><tr><td width="326" height="0" align="left" valign="top" class="coloredcell"><div class="para" label-module="para"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%90%8D%E6%BF%91%E5%8D%9A%E8%87%A3"><b>名濑博臣</b></a></div>
配音演员：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%93%83%E6%9C%A8%E8%BE%BE%E5%A4%AE">铃木达央</a>（小学时代：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%BD%90%E4%BB%93%E7%BB%AB%E9%9F%B3">佐仓绫音</a>）<div class="para" label-module="para">异界士中远近闻名的名濑家的长子。美月的哥哥。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">文艺部幽灵成员，高中3年级生。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">极度的妹控，变态中的战斗机。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">思维敏捷，分析能力很强。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">曾经似乎与秋人有些纠结，但如今是可以彼此开玩笑的关系。喜欢把双手放在神原秋人腋下取暖。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">和妹妹名濑美月一样担心着秋人和未来。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">由于异界士能力的影响导致通身害怕寒冷，时刻带着围巾，但围巾也常常作为武器使用。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">崇拜姐姐名濑泉且希望与她看齐，但表示不会采用像姐姐一样的行事方式。小说中很受学妹欢迎，动画中境界彼方事件后成为名濑家总管。</div>
</td><td valign="top" align="left" width="329"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-center" style="width:220px; float: none; display: block; margin: 0px auto; clear: both;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E5%A2%83%E7%95%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%BC%E6%96%B9/82347/0/203fb80e7bec54e7035165d7b8389b504ec26abd?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="名濑博臣" style="width:220px;height:163px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="http://f.hiphotos.baidu.com/baike/s%3D220/sign=ec799dd36159252da7171a06049a032c/203fb80e7bec54e7035165d7b8389b504ec26abd.jpg"  alt="名濑博臣" style="width:220px;height:163px;"/>
</a>
<span class="description">
名濑博臣
</span>
</div></div>
</td></tr></table><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="2_2" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub11103476_2_2" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="其他角色" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="2-2" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">境界的彼方</span>其他角色</h3>
</div>
<table log-set-param="table_view" class="table-view log-set-param transparentBorder" data-sort="sortDisabled"><tr><td width="326" height="0" align="left" valign="top" class="coloredcell"><div class="para" label-module="para"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%96%B0%E5%A0%82%E5%BD%A9%E5%8D%8E"><b>新堂彩华</b></a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">配音演员：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%BF%9B%E8%97%A4%E5%B0%9A%E7%BE%8E">进藤尚美</a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">原型是九尾狐狸的妖梦，但却以异界士为职业的怪人。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">很久以来就居住在这片土地上的很强大的妖梦。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">表面上看是在经营着点心屋（动画中是照相馆和咖啡屋，还带着一名可以变成人型的猫型妖梦新堂爱）</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">小说中很喜欢用钱调戏秋人（聊天都收费）</div>
</td><td valign="top" align="left" width="329"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-center" style="width:220px; float: none; display: block; margin: 0px auto; clear: both;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E5%A2%83%E7%95%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%BC%E6%96%B9/82347/0/bd315c6034a85edfdd9487ea48540923dc5475da?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="新堂彩华" style="width:220px;height:188px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="http://a.hiphotos.baidu.com/baike/s%3D220/sign=c7f8edbdac345982c18ae2903cf5310b/bd315c6034a85edfdd9487ea48540923dc5475da.jpg"  alt="新堂彩华" style="width:220px;height:188px;"/>
</a>
<span class="description">
新堂彩华
</span>
</div></div>
</td></tr><tr><td width="326" height="0" align="left" valign="top" class="coloredcell"><div class="para" label-module="para"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%BA%8C%E4%B9%8B%E5%AE%AB%E9%9B%AB"><b>二之宫雫</b></a></div>
配音演员：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%B8%A1%E8%BE%B9%E6%98%8E%E4%B9%83">渡边明乃</a><div class="para" label-module="para">擅长肉弹战的异界士，小说中是受聘于名濑家族的攻击专家。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">日常生活中是秋人他们学校里的老师。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">有着很爽朗性格的美人，但是残念的地方也很多。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">比如经常被男人甩。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">在胜负服装上的选择也很残念。</div>
</td><td valign="top" align="left" width="329"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-center" style="width:220px; float: none; display: block; margin: 0px auto; clear: both;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E5%A2%83%E7%95%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%BC%E6%96%B9/82347/0/5882b2b7d0a20cf41288861677094b36adaf99da?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="二之宫雫" style="width:220px;height:186px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="http://d.hiphotos.baidu.com/baike/s%3D220/sign=512b410ad6ca7bcb797bc02d8e086b3f/5882b2b7d0a20cf41288861677094b36adaf99da.jpg"  alt="二之宫雫" style="width:220px;height:186px;"/>
</a>
<span class="description">
二之宫雫
</span>
</div></div>
</td></tr><tr><td width="326" height="0" align="left" valign="top" class="coloredcell"><div class="para" label-module="para"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%97%A4%E7%9C%9F%E5%BC%A5%E5%8B%92"><b>藤真弥勒</b></a></div>
配音演员：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%9D%BE%E9%A3%8E%E9%9B%85%E4%B9%9F">松风雅也</a><div class="para" label-module="para">小说中：</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">异界士协会审问官，忍受不了老是落后于名濑泉于是生出了憎恨。利用峰岸舞耶和栗山未来、楠木右京、永水桔梗想杀死名濑泉，并让秋人暴走。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">动画中：</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">异界士协会派遣来的男人，在身体内养着妖梦。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">难以捉摸，不好对付的性格。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">时常采取可疑的行动。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">将奇怪的武器交给了伊波樱，并利用她收集妖梦的力量以强化武器。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">与名濑泉一战后不知所踪。</div>
</td><td valign="top" align="left" width="329"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-center" style="width:220px; float: none; display: block; margin: 0px auto; clear: both;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E5%A2%83%E7%95%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%BC%E6%96%B9/82347/0/0e2442a7d933c8954b62e2b2d01373f0830200de?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="藤真弥勒" style="width:220px;height:187px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="http://c.hiphotos.baidu.com/baike/s%3D220/sign=0feb9e31a686c9170c03553bf93c70c6/0e2442a7d933c8954b62e2b2d01373f0830200de.jpg"  alt="藤真弥勒" style="width:220px;height:187px;"/>
</a>
<span class="description">
藤真弥勒
</span>
</div></div>
</td></tr><tr><td width="326" height="0" align="left" valign="top" class="coloredcell"><div class="para" label-module="para"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%90%8D%E6%BF%91%E6%B3%89"><b>名濑泉</b></a></div>
配音演员：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%B7%9D%E6%BE%84%E7%BB%AB%E5%AD%90">川澄绫子</a><div class="para" label-module="para">名濑家的长女，博臣与美月的姐姐。小说中经常堆出商业笑容等各种假笑，看上去不是好人但其实为后辈们着想。动画中是冷面御姐。会陪二之宫喝酒</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">身处在精明强干的异界士中以牢笼能力出名的的名濑一族，只有少数能使用冻结界的人。苦心经营着名濑家。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">似乎也在身体中饲养妖梦，但其精神本质与藤真弥勒不同。是藤真弥勒想要与之战斗的人。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">小说中用白日梦结界制住了暴走的秋人。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">动画中比其他人更早结识栗山未来。帮助栗山未来解决伊波家的麻烦并让她来到这个城市，希望借助未来的力量消减境界的彼方。用冰冻结界将秋人体内的人类部分削弱，导致秋人妖梦化。境界彼方事件后将管理名濑家的职权交给博臣。</div>
</td><td valign="top" align="left" width="329"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-center" style="width:220px; float: none; display: block; margin: 0px auto; clear: both;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E5%A2%83%E7%95%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%BC%E6%96%B9/82347/0/7af40ad162d9f2d381455e26a8ec8a136227cca7?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="名濑泉" style="width:220px;height:168px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="http://g.hiphotos.baidu.com/baike/s%3D220/sign=7d0d4cb679f0f736dcfe4b033a54b382/7af40ad162d9f2d381455e26a8ec8a136227cca7.jpg"  alt="名濑泉" style="width:220px;height:168px;"/>
</a>
<span class="description">
名濑泉
</span>
</div></div>
</td></tr><tr><td width="326" height="0" align="left" valign="top" class="coloredcell"><div class="para" label-module="para"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%A5%9E%E5%8E%9F%E5%BC%A5%E7%94%9F"><b>神原弥生</b></a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">配音演员：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%BB%8A%E9%87%8E%E5%AE%8F%E7%BE%8E">今野宏美</a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">秋人的母亲，异界士，身世神秘。非常关心秋人的情况。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">是个有着不俗巨乳妈妈。拥有着前卫的性格，以给人惊喜为乐，现在更是把诸多事情都交给秋人自己处理，秋人为此时常感到困扰。让人十分好奇秋人的爸爸究竟是个什么样的人（会喜欢上这样的女生），</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">小说中蛋包饭技术一般，动画中不知为何在制作蛋包饭上十分的笨拙。</div>
</td><td valign="top" align="left" width="329"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-center" style="width:220px; float: none; display: block; margin: 0px auto; clear: both;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E5%A2%83%E7%95%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%BC%E6%96%B9/82347/0/5243fbf2b2119313f9add09167380cd791238d20?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="神原弥生" style="width:220px;height:187px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="http://b.hiphotos.baidu.com/baike/s%3D220/sign=103d277c57fbb2fb302b5f107f4b2043/5243fbf2b2119313f9add09167380cd791238d20.jpg"  alt="神原弥生" style="width:220px;height:187px;"/>
</a>
<span class="description">
神原弥生
</span>
</div></div>
</td></tr></table><table log-set-param="table_view" width="99%" class="transparentBorder"><tr><td align="left" valign="top"><div class="para" label-module="para"><b>峰岸舞耶</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">小说第二卷登场，外号白银狂犬，熟练地使用枪械，能力是绝对不会被人偷袭。养了一只叫“烤红薯”的蜥蜴型妖梦。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">从小被人欺负，初中时藤真弥勒交给她一把手枪并用其杀了欺负她的同学于是被异界士协会通缉，被藤真弥勒利用。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">事件解决后归入名濑家族旗下。</div>
</td><td width="100" align="center" valign="center"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E5%A2%83%E7%95%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%BC%E6%96%B9/82347/0/dbb44aed2e738bd4c93212f3a38b87d6267ff9e5?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="峰岸舞耶（晕过去的）" style="width:220px;height:165px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="http://c.hiphotos.baidu.com/baike/s%3D220/sign=d13602d9d60735fa95f049bbae500f9f/dbb44aed2e738bd4c93212f3a38b87d6267ff9e5.jpg"  alt="峰岸舞耶（晕过去的）" style="width:220px;height:165px;"/>
</a>
<span class="description">
峰岸舞耶（晕过去的）
</span>
</div></div>
</td></tr></table><div class="para" label-module="para"><sup>[4]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[4]_11103476">&nbsp;</a>
</div>
<table log-set-param="table_view" data-sort="sortDisabled"><tr><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><b>真城优斗</b></td><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1">身材高瘦的少年，未来的青梅竹马。有操控下级妖梦的能力。</td></tr><tr><td width="327" align="left" valign="middle"><b>楠木右京</b></td><td width="328" align="left" valign="middle">小说第二卷登场，异界士协会审问官。父母被妖梦杀死所以极度痛恨妖梦，被藤真弥勒利用</td></tr><tr><td width="327" align="left" valign="middle"><b>永水桔梗</b></td><td width="328" align="left" valign="middle">小说第二卷登场，异界士协会审问官。被藤真弥勒利用</td></tr><tr><td width="327" align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><b>一之宫庵</b></td><td width="328" align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1">专精于情报的异界士，能将自己的意识直接连上网络。</td></tr></table><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="3" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub11103476_3" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="用语解说" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">境界的彼方</span>用语解说</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="3" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%A6%96%E6%A2%A6/16414941" data-lemmaid="16414941"><b>妖梦</b></a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">在这个世界上徘徊着的异形之物。其姿态千变万化，是从人类的怨恨而生的。其中也存在着以人类为食的种类。一般的人是看不到它们的身影的。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>异界士</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">以讨伐妖梦为业的人们。依靠血统使能力流传下去。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>异界士协会</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">异界士们所属的组织。只要在协会登录就会被认作异界士。不知是谁为了什么意图而设立的。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>妖梦石</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">消灭妖梦后掉落的石头，其体形很大却有许多不同的形状，详细情形未知。存在着认为它是妖梦的核心的说法。异界士在鉴定这些石头后，会把它拿去换钱或者别的报酬，但也有的异界士似乎用其强化武器，如伊波樱。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>半妖</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">是人类与妖梦结合而出生的稀有的存在，不过由于其数量过于稀少，其存在大多不为人知。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>名濑家</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">拥有操纵牢笼（也有可能是屏障之类的）的血统的一族，自古以来常年进行着对周边的土地管理、保护等工作。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>牢笼</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">名濑一族血脉相传的能力，这种能力能够切割空间，所以既可以用来攻击也可以用来防御。另外，因为能够切割部分空间，就如同结界一般，可以阻止其他东西进入。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>烤番薯</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">美月偷偷养的妖梦，因为长的像松软的红薯，所以被命名成“烤番薯”。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>虚无之影</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">没有实体的强大的妖梦。能够附身在实力弱的异界士身上。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>长月市花野寺镇</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">秋人他们居住的小镇。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>境界的彼方</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">在蛰伏期显现出其部分姿态。是比虚无之影更为强大的妖梦，被认为是千万年来人类负面情绪的产物集合，拥有将世界引向毁灭的巨大威力。神原秋人的妖梦部分被认为是其另一部分。<sup>[5]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[5]_11103476">&nbsp;</a>
</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="4" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub11103476_4" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="出版信息" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
